l rules after rare accidents, and regulatory bots that update financial compliance logic in response to new fraud typologies. By treating rule refinement as a *learned, reflective process* rather than a symbolic compilation, MERIT achieves higher adaptability without sacrificing explainability—each edit is traceable to precedent and justified by contextual feedback. This represents a paradigm shift from reactive rule updating to anticipatory, experience-driven normative reasoning.",
